These visuals made complex data simple, allowing decision-makers to see key insights at a glance.

Recommendations and Observations
Invest more in Naypyitaw, expand branches or run loyalty campaigns in the top-performing city.
Enhance Food & Beverages promotions, focus on upselling premium options or bundled offers.
Encourage digital payments, offer discounts for E-wallet or credit card users to balance payment preferences.
Improve “average” customer experiences use feedback surveys to understand what’s missing.
Personalize marketing by gender, female customers show higher spending in key categories like fashion and food.
Conclusion
Boku Super Mart’s 2024 sales data revealed more than numbers it told a story of where the store shines and where it can grow.

By focusing on city performance, customer satisfaction, and modern payment trends, Boku is set to turn insights into smarter strategies for 2025.
Data isn’t just for analysis it’s a mirror showing what’s working and what’s worth improving.

